[SHORT DESC]
Heals 50% max HP after 2 turns.

[LONG DESC]
<p>Whichever Pokémon is active in the user's position at the end of the second turn recovers 50% of its maximum HP. If the Pokémon in the user's position is KOed on that turn, the Pokemon that switches in will not be healed by Wish.</p>
